The given equation is equivalent to $|y| = \frac{10 - |x|}{2},$ or
\[y = \begin{cases} \frac{10 - x}{2}, & -10 \le x \le 0, \\ \frac{x + 10}{2}, & 0 \le x \le 10. \end{cases}\][asy]
